title: Beauty World The Musical Soundtrack 2015
description:
Beauty World is a Singaporean musical written by Michael Chiang and composed by Dick Lee. Drawing on the tradition of 1950s black-and-white Cantonese movies, it tells the story of a young Malaysian girl who comes from Batu Pahat to 1960s Singapore in search of her father and winds up in the eponymous sleazy night club.

Music/Lyrics - Dick Lee
Arranger - Indra Shahrir Ismail
Vocal Producer - John Lee
